OL,3,CInquest opened into death of school
OL,4,Cpupil in Windermere
OL,6,FAn inquest has been formally opened
OL,7,Finto the death of a schoolboy who is
OL,8,Fbelieved to have drowned while on an
OL,9,Fend-of-term trip to Windermere.
OL,11,FCockermouth Coroner's Court heard on
OL,12,FTuesday that Abuzr Mirza lost his life
OL,13,Fjust four days after his 16th
OL,14,Fbirthday, on 25 July.
OL,16,FRobert Cohen, one of His Majesty's
OL,17,Fcoroners for Cumbria, gave some brief
OL,18,Fcircumstances as he opened an inquest
OL,19,Finto the teenager's death during a
OL,20,Fshort hearing.
