OL,3,CInquest opened into death of school
OL,4,Cpupil in Windermere
OL,6,FAbuzr, of Burnley, Lancashire, had
OL,7,Fattended the Brockhole at Windermere,
OL,8,Fon the north east shore of England's
OL,9,Flargest lake, while on a school visit.
OL,11,F"In the course of that trip he took
OL,12,Fshoes and socks off to enter the lake
OL,13,Fto paddle, and got into difficulty and
OL,14,Fappears to have drowned in the course
OL,15,Fof that activity," said Mr Cohen, who
OL,16,Fdeemed it appropriate to open the
OL,17,Finquest.
