OL,6,FThe coroner added: "I have been made
OL,7,Faware by Cumbria police that they are
OL,8,Fconducting further inquiries into the
OL,9,Fcircumstances of Mr Mirza's death. In
OL,10,Fthose circumstances it is appropriate
OL,11,Fthat I should suspend further
OL,12,Finvestigation by the coroners' service
OL,13,Fpending the outcome of the enquiries
OL,14,Fof other agencies."
OL,16,FThe inquest was formally suspended.
