OL,6,FA signed and dated statement submitted
OL,7,Fby Abuzr's father, Osman Beg,
OL,8,Fconfirming the identity of his son,
OL,9,Fwas formally admitted into evidence by
OL,10,Fthe coroner.
OL,12,FMr Cohen concluded the hearing by
OL,13,Fsaying: "I send to all of Mr Mirza's
OL,14,Ffamily, friends and loved ones the
OL,15,Fcourt's profound sympathy and
OL,16,Fcondolences."
