OL,6,FA spokesman for the school Abuzr
OL,7,Fattended had said after his death:
OL,8,F"Abuzr was a lovely pupil who touched
OL,9,Fthe lives of many with his warmth and
OL,10,Fkindness."
OL,12,FIn a Facebook tribute, the teen's
OL,13,Ffather had said: "He was and still is
OL,14,Fa perfect son, I wish everyone is
OL,15,Fblessed with a son like my son."
